    56→### 3. Добавить depends_on / blocks\n    57→Формат в task.md:\n    58→```yaml\n    59→depends_on:\n    60→  - \"CORE-001\"\n    61→blocks:\n    62→  - \"CORE-005\"\n    63→```\n    64→Проверка перед стартом: если есть незавершённые зависимости → статус BLOCKED\n    65→\n    66→### 4. Skill list_tasks\n    67→Показать список задач с фильтрацией:\n    68→```\n    69→/list_tasks status=ready_for_dev priority=1,2\n    70→```\n    71→\n    72→## Context\n    73→\n    74→- Skills directory: `/skills/`\n    75→- Existing skills: task_management, make_task, perform_task\n    76→- Task format needs to be backward compatible\n    77→\n    78→## Constraints\n    79→\n    80→- Не ломать существующий workflow\n    81→- Обратная совместимость с текущими задачами\n    82→- Использовать YAML frontmatter для метаданных\n    83→\n    84→## Acceptance Criteria\n    85→\n    86→- [x] Extended task.md format with YAML frontmatter documented in task_management skill\n    87→- [x] BLOCKED status added to workflow\n    88→- [x] depends_on/blocks mechanism documented\n    89→- [x] list_tasks skill created with filtering support\n    90→- [x] Update existing tasks to new format\n    91→- [x] Update make_task skill for new format\n    92→- [x] Update perform_task skill with dependency checking\n    93→\n    94→## Artifacts\n    95→\n    96→- Updated: `/skills/task_management/SKILL.md`\n    97→- Updated: `/skills/make_task/SKILL.md`\n    98→- Updated: `/skills/perform_task/SKILL.md`\n    99→- Created: `/skills/list_tasks/SKILL.md`\n   100→\n   101→## Team Specification\n   102→\n   103→| Role | Agent |\n   104→|------|-------|\n   105→| Developer | senior-android-developer |\n   106→| Reviewer | android-code-reviewer |\n   107→| QA | qa-expert |\n   108→\n   109→## Status: Ready for review\n   110→## Updated: 2026-03-05 11:00:00\n   111→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malw